---
title: Sticky King Prawn Noodle Stir-Fry  with Carrot, Onion and Green Beans
description: Mango chutney, ketchup and soy sauce are the unexpected heroes of tonight’s stir-fry sauce. When it comes to creating amazing flavours, Chef André rarely gets it wrong. As a father of two, he’s no stranger to fussy eaters and is constantly on the lookout for ways he can get his kids to try new foods. Packed with hidden veggies and on the table in 35 minutes, this is a recipe the whole family will love. Enjoy!
